                Marcellus <lb n="2"/>et Caius <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> Pentii <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>enturionis</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilii</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>eq</abbr><ex>uites</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>al</abbr><ex>ae</ex></expan> I <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> Mar<lb break="no" n="6"/>ti <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olverunt</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibentes</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Abweichungen in der Lesung; verbesserte, aber immer noch problematische Lesung von Gómez Pantoja. Zu Penius vgl. AE 1976, 0304.</p>
